---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-950 dark:text-zinc-50 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-zinc-500 mb-10">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>
    <div class="tda-prose">
      <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how The Daily Algorithm collects, uses, and protects information.</p>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you post a comment, we collect your display name and message only. No email or account is required. Emoji reactions are recorded anonymously without any identifying information.</p>
      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>Comment data is stored securely and may be displayed publicly on the article after moderation. We do not sell, trade, or share personal information with third parties.</p>
      <h2>Local Storage</h2>
      <p>We store your theme preference (light or dark mode) in your browser's local storage. No tracking cookies are used.</p>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use Supabase for database services and Vercel for hosting. These services maintain their own privacy policies.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact <a href="mailto:hello@thedailyalgorithm.com">hello@thedailyalgorithm.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>